    <p>
        MVVM Tools is available in Visual Studio 2015 or later via Tools &gt; Extensions and Updates, or on the <a href="https://visualstudiogallery.msdn.microsoft.com/978ed555-9f0d-44a2-884c-9084844ac469">Visual Studio Gallery</a>.
