    <p>Please direct all discussions to the <a href="https://github.com/cbordeman/Mvvm-Tools/issues">GitHub Issues Page</a>.
    </p>
    <p/>
    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Press Ctrl+E,V to switch between your view and view model.</li>
        <li>Ability to configure the location of views and view models base on the selected project. This allows different modules to use different MVVM schemes.</li>
        <li>Ability to scaffold new views and view models based on your MVVM configuration and a selected template.</li>
        <li>Access to View + View Model templates maintained by the community.</li>
        <li>Your team can also maintain a set of templates in a local folder as a set of .tpl files.</li>
    </ul>
